<A>__{jeffrey alone on the jetty, looking out to sea. trying to decide, trying to untangle identity and consequence. a moment. he turns, crossing to lowell and scruggs. then. it's the three men, standing on the lawn. time seems to slow...all of them aware it's a critical decision, personally and historically...}
